To create wallet			solana-keygen new --outfile ~/my-keypair.json

To check pubkey-			solana-keygen pubkey ~/my-keypair.json	or	solana address

To verify keypair-			solana-keygen verify (Pubkey/address) ~/my-keypair.json

To enter Devnet-			solana config set --url https://api.devnet.solana.com --keypair ~/my-keypair.json

To enter Mainnet-		solana config set --url https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com --keypair

To confirm Devnet-		solana config get	

To airdrop Solana-		solana airdrop 2

To check Solana Balance- 		solana balance

To create token-			spl-token create-token	{Then get token address}
 
To create account-		spl-token create-account (token address)

To mint token-			spl-token mint (token address) (Number of tokens)
 
To check accounts-		spl-token accounts

To get address-			spl-token address

To transfer-			spl-token transfer (Token address) 50 Person’s address



				spl-token transfer --fund-recipient (Token address) 50 Person’s 				address --allow-unfunded-recipient


To disable future minting-		spl-token authorize {token address} mint --disable

